vation:** All 8 ACs are cli-verifiable via unit tests — no external dependencies.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":6,"oldLines":3,"newStart":6,"newLines":10,"lines":[" - **Missing context:** `InitResult` in `types.ts` may need `stacks` field but epic FR4 doesn't explicitly call it out — implied by scope."," - **Risk:** `detectStacks()` can return duplicate stack names from multiple directories. `stacks` field needs deduplication."," - **Observation:** All 8 ACs are cli-verifiable via unit tests — no external dependencies.","+","+### 9-2-state-schema-migration-multi-stack — dev-story (2026-03-23T14:32Z)","+","+- **Pre-existing type errors:** `bridge.test.ts` implicit `any`, `run.test.ts` spread arg type error, `stack.test.ts` missing `endpoint`, `status.test.ts` missing `timeoutSummary`. None from this story.","+- **Workaround:** Used `stacks: ['nodejs'] as StackName[]` instead of `as const` in `stack.test.ts` because readonly tuples aren't assignable to `StackName[]`.","+- **Risk:** `recoverCorruptedState()` recovery path not directly unit-tested for `stacks` field — would need planted `package.json` in temp dir.","+- **Observation:** 19 new tests added, all 3098 tests pass with 0 failures."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
